projects:
[{'title': 'Student Consultant for DAMCO Logistics', 'date': {'start': {'month': 2, 'day': None, 'year': 2017}, 'end': {'month': 5, 'day': None, 'year': 2017}}, 'description': 'As part of the bachelor programme International Studies at Leiden University, which I have graduated from, I took part in a "Student Consultancy" project. My team and I worked together with "Damco", a company providing air and ocean freight services, as well as additional services as for instance insurance and warehousing. Our tasks as consultants were to research and find a way for the enterprise to adapt their operations to future developments within the markets.This meant that we, as student consultants, had to identify and analyse any possible future shifts in the market and transportation industry, and create a suitable, well-thought-out business plan for Damco and their future operations. 

This project went on for several months and included several meetings with the representatives of Damco to discuss their needs and requests, and of course close, active teamwork with my colleagues. This has given me a lot of insight in both what it means to take part in consultancy and assure that you meet the wishes of the client, as well as which factors all come together in deciding what the future course of a firm will be.

Finally, when my colleagues and I finalized our work, we were asked to present it alongside all other teams, and take part in a '"competition" that would decide which group of student consultants had provided the best work. When presenting our business plan the representatives of Damco, our professors and fellow students, Damco received our plan with great enthusiasm, and as a consequence, my colleagues and I were granted with the first place and won the overall competition, besides also delivering Damco with an effective, satisfying business plan.', 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Demi', 'last_name': 'Donninger', 'name': None, 'headline': 'China Analyst & Public Relations at Datenna'}]}]
